226
00:12:54,440 --> 00:12:55,400
Alright, I gotta go.

227
00:12:57,120 --> 00:12:57,830
Shang Bao.

228
00:13:04,120 --> 00:13:04,510
Well...

229
00:13:05,670 --> 00:13:07,310
