230
00:13:09,990 --> 00:13:12,150
Ms. Fang, I know you mean well.

231
00:13:12,280 --> 00:13:13,790
But I'm a grown man.

232
00:13:13,790 --> 00:13:14,600
Don't worry.

233
00:13:14,990 --> 00:13:16,560
I'm actually looking to hire.

234
00:13:16,760 --> 00:13:18,240
My resto is doing pretty well.

235
00:13:18,560 --> 00:13:19,880
