keep track of the books,

237
00:13:23,790 --> 00:13:24,790
handle the customers,

238
00:13:25,510 --> 00:13:27,440
and clean the whole place.

239
00:13:28,350 --> 00:13:29,880
Plus, I still need to
look after Tongtong.

240
00:13:30,310 --> 00:13:32,120
Honestly, it's just too much for me.

241
00:13:32,760 --> 00:13:34,440
I think you're hardworking,

242
00:13:34,440 --> 00:13:35,310
and reliable too.

243
00:13:35,310 --> 00:13:36,280
That's why I asked you.

244
00:13:38,040 --> 00:13:39,720
We can talk about salary.
It's flexible.

245
00:13:39,720 --> 00:13:40,920
So...

246
00:13:40,920 --> 00:13:41,630
