eat my resto out of business?

253
00:13:50,150 --> 00:13:51,190
Hey, you never know.

254
00:13:51,190 --> 00:13:52,790
You know how much I can eat.

255
00:13:57,080 --> 00:13:57,880
Ms. Fang,

256
00:13:58,080 --> 00:13:59,120
I'll get going now.

257
00:13:59,440 --> 00:14:00,670
I'll start work here tomorrow.

258
00:14:00,760 --> 00:14:01,880
Shang Bao.

